text:

name: Tonya Whitehead
text: Meagan is an outstanding pharmacist.  She always goes way beyond the call of duty to make sure that the customers have her undivided attention.  I have MS and she is always very attentive to my questions and gives me the answers in a way that she knows that I can understand.  She is the BEST
